Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.15,0:07:29.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}内人反复交代我要把这个交给冬月教授
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.76,0:07:30.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}她相当尊敬您呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.70,0:07:33.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}那真是我的荣幸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.70,0:07:34.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}唯现在怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.30,0:07:36.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}没有参加这次旅程吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.64,0:07:39.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}唯也一直很想来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.76,0:07:41.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}但是现在她有了孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.20,0:07:45.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}你的组织叫什么 SEELE 对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.21,0:07:47.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}负面传闻不断呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.14,0:07:50.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}对理事会施压可令人不敢恭维
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.97,0:07:53.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}您的洁癖主义还是一点儿都没变
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.10,0:07:56.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}在这个时代，干净的组织根本无法存活啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.31,0:07:59.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}这次关于第二次冲击的正式调查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.28,0:08:03.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}如果调查队都是 SEELE 的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.44,0:08:04.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}将会产生各式各样的麻烦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.00,0:08:08.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}我们就是用于此的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.57,0:08:13.82,screen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【NERV 总部·第 4 隔离设施】
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.28,0:08:16.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}我还是不习惯待在黑暗的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.63,0:08:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}总是回想起讨厌的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.57,0:08:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}她是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.63,0:08:22.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}那个调查队中唯一的生还者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.20,0:08:25.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}名叫葛城美里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.35,0:08:26.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}葛城
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.44,0:08:28.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}葛城博士的千金吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.41,0:08:29.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.32,0:08:32.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}已将近两年没有开过口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.05,0:08:33.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}真可怜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.30,0:08:35.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}毕竟她亲眼看到了那地狱般的场面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.36,0:08:37.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}就算身体的创伤治好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.02,0:08:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}心里的伤也没这么容易就痊愈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.76,0:08:42.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}是啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.27,0:08:45.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}我们的调查结果也没那么容易出炉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.27,0:08:47.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}还有这个发光的巨人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.10,0:08:48.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}这次事件真是一堆谜团呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.53,0:08:50.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}后来联合国正式发表声明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.78,0:08:55.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}宣称第二次冲击是大质量陨石坠落所引起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.25,0:08:58.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}可是，在我看来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.20,0:09:01.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}那很明显是情报操作的结果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.50,0:09:06.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}背后隐藏着 SEELE ，还有那个叫基尔的人物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.67,0:09:10.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}我很想知道事件的真相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.93,0:09:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}就算当事人中有碇唯的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.22,0:09:19.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}为什么隐瞒巨人的存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.68,0:09:21.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}第二次冲击…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.16,0:09:23.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}你们早就知道了不是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.30,0:09:25.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}知道那天会发生那件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.07,0:09:31.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}你说你运气好，在事件前一天回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.32,0:09:35.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}那带着所有资料一起回来也是因为幸运吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.95,0:09:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}这些东西竟然没有被销毁掉，真意外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.75,0:09:44.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}我从各方面查了你的资产
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.47,0:09:47.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}养育小孩或许要花不少钱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.81,0:09:50.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}但以个人拥有的来说，金额未免太多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.03,0:09:52.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}不愧是冬月教授
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.93,0:09:54.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}您不如转到经济系教书
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.52,0:09:57.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}我要把隐藏在第二次冲击背后的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.66,0:10:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}SEELE 和死海古卷公诸于世
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.42,0:10:03.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}我不想原谅引发那件事的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.22,0:10:04.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}随您喜欢吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.53,0:10:08.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}但我想请您先看一些东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.13,0:10:12.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}这里真是很深啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.05,0:10:13.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}您感到不安吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.55,0:10:15.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}多少有一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.03,0:10:18.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}这是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.89,0:10:21.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}是我们以外不知什么人留下来的空间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.18,0:10:24.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}虽然 89% 都被埋住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.12,0:10:27.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}原本是完美的球状地底空间吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.72,0:10:32.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}那就是倾尽人类所有建立的设施
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.56,0:10:41.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}哎呀，冬月老师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.00,0:10:43.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}赤木，你竟然也来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.06,0:10:49.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}这里是探索生物计算机基础理论的最佳地点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.83,0:10:53.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}我打算将其命名为 MAGI
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.69,0:10:54.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}MAGI
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.53,0:10:56.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}来自东方的三贤者吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.20,0:10:58.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}想给我看的东西就是这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.31,0:10:59.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.64,0:11:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}请往这边走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.93,0:11:03.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}律子，我马上回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.26,0:11:07.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}这是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.52,0:11:09.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}难道是那个巨人吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.11,0:11:12.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}我们 Gehirn 把那个物体称为亚当
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.47,0:11:14.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}但是这个不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.02,0:11:16.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}不是原始的那个亚当
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.38,0:11:18.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}那它是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.13,0:11:19.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.20,0:11:22.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}这是人类利用亚当制造的东西，叫做 EVA
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.42,0:11:23.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}EVA…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.54,0:11:26.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}我们的亚当再生计划
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.04,0:11:30.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}通称 E 计划的雏型机 EVA 零号机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.42,0:11:32.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}神的原型吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.37,0:11:33.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}冬月
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.62,0:11:37.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}要不要跟我一起创造人类新的历史
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.43,0:11:47.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}那个…前辈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.16,0:11:49.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.70,0:11:51.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}快点进行丽的再测试吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.87,0:11:53.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}今天都没看到葛城小姐呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.11,0:11:55.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}啊？是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.83,0:11:57.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}葛城
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.02,0:12:00.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}嗯，葛城美里，请多多指教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.81,0:12:02.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.11,0:12:05.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}前几天我认识一个叫葛城美里的女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.12,0:12:08.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}其他人只敢远远看着我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.74,0:12:11.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}那个时候我就感觉到妈妈的名字有多响亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.24,0:12:15.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}不知为何只有她在面对我的时候毫无顾忌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.16,0:12:20.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}据说她是那个调查队中唯一生还的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.93,0:12:22.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}好像有段时间患了失语症
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.07,0:12:26.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}仿佛要填补那段空白似的，现在她常常喋喋不休
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.05,0:12:28.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}小律
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.23,0:12:31.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}我这边还是老样子整天躲在地底下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.31,0:12:34.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}配给的便当已经吃厌了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.90,0:12:37.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}上面好像依照第 2 迁都计划
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.02,0:12:39.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}开始了第 3 新东京市的建造
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.04,0:12:44.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}最近因为美里没来大学，我逼她说出理由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.06,0:12:45.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}结果原因有够愚蠢的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.68,0:12:48.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}她好像跟男友一直睡在公寓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.53,0:12:52.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}毫不厌倦的混了一个星期
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.03,0:12:55.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}我觉得自己发现了她令人意外的一面
